<div style="display:inline-block; text-align:center; ">
<h1>Candle Safety Tips</h1>
<ul>
<li>Never leave a burning candle unattended.  </li>
<li>Keep out of reach of children and pets. </li>
<li>Never move a candle while it is burning.</li>
<li>Always burn candles on a stable, heat resistant surface and away from flammable objects</li>
<li>Keep wick trimmed to about 1/4 inch to avoid excessive flame height. </li>
<li>Use a snuffer or carefully blow out the candle and quickly place the lid on to extinguish the wick if it is still partially lit.</li>
</ul>
</div>
